Package io.github.pr0methean.betterrandom.util.spliterator

Implementations of Spliterator and unboxed-primitive equivalents that wrap a Supplier or the unboxed-primitive equivalent.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractSupplierSpliterator<TSupplier,TConsumer,TSplitInto>
    An unordered, concurrent spliterator (possibly unboxed) that invokes a supplier (possibly unboxed) to get its values.
    DoubleSupplierSpliterator
    An unordered, concurrent Spliterator.OfDouble that invokes a DoubleSupplier to get its values.
    IntSupplierSpliterator
    An unordered, concurrent Spliterator.OfInt that invokes an IntSupplier to get its values.
    LongSupplierSpliterator
    An unordered, concurrent Spliterator.OfLong that invokes a LongSupplier to get its values.
